{"id": 2870, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你都遇到过哪些信息转移/同步难题？", "description": "来说说你每次换账号/换手机/存文件的时候都被哪些小麻烦打击过。（题图来自: iStock © cosmaa）", "record_count": 9729, "comment_count": 40, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190401161837r4ohQISYWHFqCGel.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-03T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5615, "title": "现如今你都遇到过哪些信息转移/同步难题？", "content": "上网时，你都遇到过哪些信息转移/同步难题？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 336943, "content": "账号解绑/改密码，收验证码的旧手机号已经注销了", "image": "img/option/option/20190401224628fEIAtrqoNbLe1YZB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 336936, "content": "每次换手机都会忘记各种密码，只能重置账号", "image": "img/option/option/20190401224617pja6RHWouyiqNhLT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 336969, "content": "很多手机浏览器都不支持导出收藏夹", "image": "img/option/option/20190401224735T3StpuJU2mnkXDKs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 336971, "content": "用 QQ 或微信传图给自己，图片经常会被压缩", "image": "img/option/option/201904012242125XQlDbRAfF27cnKr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 336953, "content": "微信不能直接下载语音，只能放到收藏里听", "image": "img/option/option/20190401224820cM25jUsKo3uZ6lrH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 336970, "content": "玩手游，安卓和苹果账号不能互通", "image": "img/option/option/201904012247236ur8jb5PTEd347BR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 336945, "content": "很多应用只有安卓或 iOS 一种版本", "image": "img/option/option/20190401224642A7yebP9tLuqs6lKH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 336954, "content": "手机里的文件太杂，备份到电脑要花很长时间", "image": "img/option/option/20190401224713Bdixab7L2HuEVlSU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 336951, "content": "每换一次设备，桌面、铃声、主题都要重设一遍", "image": "img/option/option/20190401224657t2A9gJSQmOuca3li.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}